function maximum (a)
    local mi = 1             -- æœ€å¤§å€¼ç´¢å¼•
    local m = a[mi]          -- æœ€å¤§å€¼
    for i,val in ipairs(a) do
       if val > m then
           mi = i
           m = val
       end
    end
    return m, mi
end

function factorial1(n)
    if n == 0 then
        return 1
    else
        return n * factorial1(n - 1)
    end
end
